title: MILLION DOLLAZ WORTH OF GAME EP: 53 "CORONAVIRUS, JAIL TIME + BLACK & MILDS"
description:
On this episode of Million Dollaz Worth of Game, Gillie and Wallo talk about how they are handling the Coronovirus and isolation, talk about Wallo losing virginity, and let their first follower ( @Dntcalmewhitgrl) take a shot at the third mic.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/mworthofgame
